text: Novopavlovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Isyangulovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 649 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 2 km from Isyangulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Novopavlovka, Republic of Bashkortostan
